1. CMAKE generation

    1.1 Crate folder for build files and enter there:

    mkdir build
    cd build

    1.2 Generate makefiles

    cmake ../

2. BUILD soluton
    
    In build folder call:

    make

3. Recompile and execute test

    make run

Classes adivce:

    In "BowlingGame.h" you can find an example implementation of a bowling game.

    In "BowlingTDDProject.cpp" you can find tests implementation for the mentioned class.
